{
  "texts": [
    "However, there are other challenges regarding the valid classification of tweets.",
    "For instance, the query OBAMA INJURED aiming to detect a misinformation story that Obama was injured during an attack on the White House (see Additional file 1) potentially also yields results that contradict the claim (e.g., 'Obama was not injured!')",
    "or which use irony to debunk it (e.g., 'Obama was injured?",
    "then I will move into the White House!').",
    "Our manual annotation results confirmed that the ACR method successfully retrieves a large majority of story-supporting tweets."
  ]
}